\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The SAE Institute is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution is currently offering a Higher Certificate in Digital Film Production and a Higher Certificate in Audio Production. The institution has also applied for a Bachelor of Sound Production.\line \cell \pard 

